## IF ANYTHING FAILS

**If SQL fails:**
- Check Supabase connection
- Verify SQL syntax (copy again from Obsidian file)
- Check that old tables actually need deleting

**If files won't delete:**
- Close all open files in VS Code
- Check file permissions
- Use git rm instead of manual delete

**If mobile doesn't work:**
- Check console errors
- Clear node_modules: rm -rf node_modules && npm install
- Restart Expo server

**If git commit fails:**
- Check you have uncommitted changes: git status
- Ensure git is configured: git config --list

